// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2309 — Mass File Rename (abyss)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 7fa0faf1-bb3e-5c5a-9ca1-fba1d6ce1109

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
